quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  31,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  31,1,Alif Laaam Meeem
  31,2,yeh hikmat ki ( bhari hui ) kitaab ki ayatain hain
  31,3,naiko karon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
  31,4,jo namaz ki pabandi karte aur zakaat dete aur akhirat ka yaqeen rakhtay hain
  31,5,yahi apne perwar-digaar ( ki taraf ) se hadaayat par hain aur yahi nijaat panay walay hain
  31,6,aur logon mein baaz aisa hai jo behooda hikaytein kharidata hai taakay ( logon ko ) be samjhay khuda ke raste se gumraah kere aur is seistehzaa kere yahi log hain jin ko zaleel karne wala azaab hoga
  31,7,aur jab is ko hamari ayatain sunai jati hain to akarr kar munh phair laita hai goya unn ko suna hi nahi jaisay unn ke kaanon mein saqal hai to is ko dard dainay walay azaab ki khushkhabri suna do
  31,8,jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay unn ke liye Nemat ke baagh hain
  31,9,hamesha unn mein rahen ge. khuda ka wada sacha hai aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
  31,10,usi ne asmano ko satonon ke baghair pedakiya jaissa ke tum dekhte ho aur zameen par pahar ( bana kar ) rakh diye taakay tum ko hila hila nah day aur is mein har terhan ke janwar phela diye. aur hum hi ne asmano se pani nazilkiya phir ( uss se ) is mein har qisam ki nafees cheeze agayiN
  31,11,yeh to khuda ki paidaiesh hai to mujhe dikhao ke khuda ke siwa jo log hain onhon nekiya pedakiya hai? haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh zalim Sarih gumraahi mein hain
  31,12,aur hum ne luqman ko danai bakhsh. ke khuda ka shukar karo. aur jo shakhs shukar karta hai to apne hi faiday ke liye shukar karta hai. aur jo nashukri karta hai to khuda bhi be parwa aur sazawar hamd (o sana ) hai
  31,13,aur ( uss waqt ko yaad karo ) jab luqman ne apne betay ko nasiyaat karte hue kaha ke beta khuda ke sath shirk nah karna. shirk to bara ( bhaari ) zulm hai
  31,14,aur hum ne ensaan ko jisay uss ki maa takleef par takleef seh kar pait mein uthaiye rakhti hai ( phir is ko doodh plati hai ) aur ( aakhir kaar ) do baras mein is ka doodh chhurana hota hai ( apne neez ) is ke maa baap ke baray mein takeed ki hai ke mera bhi shukar karta reh aur apne maa baap ka bhi ( ke tum ko ) meri hi taraf lout kar aana hai
  31,15,aur agar woh tairay darpay hon ke to mere sath kisi aisi cheez ko shareek kere jis ka tujhe kuch bhi ilm nahi to un ka kaha nah maanna. haan duniya ( ke kamon ) mein un ka achi terhan sath dena aur jo shakhs meri taraf rujoo laaye is ke raste par chalna phir tum ko meri taraf lout kar aana hai. to jo kaam tum karte rahay mein sab se tum ko aagah karoon ga
  31,16,( luqman ne yeh bhi kaha ke ) beta agar koi amal ( bil farz ) rai ke danay ke barabar bhi ( chhota ) ho aur ho bhi kisi pathar ke andar ya asmano mein ( makhfi ho ) ya zameen mein. khuda uss ko qayamat ke din laa maujood kere ga. kuch shak nahi ke khuda bareek bain ( aur ) khabardaar hai
  31,17,beta namaz ki pabandi rakhna aur ( logon ko ) achay kamon ke karne ka amar aur buri baton se mana karte rehna aur jo museebat tujh par waqay ho is par sabr karna. bay shak yeh barri himmat ke kaam hain
  31,18,aur ( Azrah ghuroor ) logon se gaal nah phulana aur zameen mein akarr kar nah chalna. ke khuda kisi itranay walay khud pasand ko pasand nahi karta
  31,19,aur apni chaal mein aitdaal kiye rehna aur ( boltay waqt ) aawaz neechi rakhna kyunkay ( umchee aawaz gadhon ki hai aur kuch shak nahi ke ) sab awazon se burii aawaz gadhon ki hai
  31,20,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab ko khuda ne tumahray qaboo mein kar diya hai aur tum par apni zahiri aur baatini naematain poori kar di hain. aur baaz log aisay hain ke khuda ke baray mein jhagarte hain nah ilm rakhtay hain aur nah hadaayat aur nah kitaab roshan
  31,21,aur jab unn se kaha jata hai ke jo ( kitaab ) khuda ne nazil farmai hai uss ki pairwi karo. to kehte hain ke hum to isi ki pairwi karen ge jis par apne baap dada ko paaya. bhala agarchay shetan un ko dozakh ke azaab ki taraf bulaataa ho ( tab bhi? )
  31,22,aur jo shakhs apne tain khuda ka farmanbardar kardey aur nekokaar bhi ho to uss ne mazboot dastaweez haath mein le li. aur ( sab ) kamon ka injaam khuda hi ki taraf hai
  31,23,aur jo kufar kere to uss ka kufar tumhe ghumnaak nah kardey un ko hamari taraf lout kar aana hai phir jo kaam wohkiya karte they hum unn ko jta yin ge. bay shak khuda dilon ki baton se waaqif hai
  31,24,hum unn ko thora sa faida p_hnchayin ge phir azaab shadeed ki taraf majaboor kar ke لیجائیں ge
  31,25,aur agar tum unn se pucho ke asmano aur zameen ko kis ne pedakiya to bol uthen ge ke khuda ne. keh do ke khuda ka shukar hai lekin un mein aksar samajh nahi rakhtay
  31,26,jo kuch asmano aur zameen mein hai ( sab ) khuda hi ka hai. bay shak khuda be parwa aur saza waar hamd (o sana ) hai
  31,27,aur agar yun ho ke zameen mein jitne darakht hain ( sab ke sab ) qalam hon aur samandar ( ka tamam pani ) siyahi ho ( aur ) is ke baad saat samandar aur ( siyahi ho jayen ) to khuda ki baatein ( yani is ki sftin ) khatam nah hon. bay shak khuda ghalib hikmat wala hai
  31,28,( khuda ko ) tumhara peda karna aur jِla uthana 1 shakhs ( ke peda karne aur jala aُthane ) ki terhan hai. bay shak khuda suneney wala dekhnay wala hai
  31,29,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke khuda hi raat ko din mein daakhil karta hai aur ( wohi ) din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai aur usi ne Sooraj aur chaand ko ( tumahray ) zair farmaan kar rakha hai. har aik aik waqt e muqarrar taq chal raha hai aur yeh ke khuda tumahray sab aamaal se khabardaar hai
  31,30,yeh is liye ke khuda ki zaat brhq hai aur jin ko yeh log khuda ke siwa pkarte hain woh laghu hain aur yeh ke khuda hi aliiiii rutba aur graami qader hai
  31,31,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke khuda hi ki meharbani se kashtiyan darya mein chalti hain. taakay woh tum ko apni kuch nishanain dukhaay. bay shak is mein har sabr karne walay ( aur ) shukar karne walay ke liye nishanain hain
  31,32,aur jab unn par ( darya ki ) laharen saybanon ki terhan chhaa jati hain to khuda ko pukarnay ( aur ) khalis is ki ibadat karne lagtay hain phir jab woh unn ko nijaat day kar khushki par pouncha deta hai to baaz hi insaaf par qaim rehtay hain. aur hamari nshanyon se wohi inkaar karte hain jo ehad shikan aur nashukray hain
  31,33,logo apne perwar-digaar se daro aur uss din ka khauf karo ke nah to baap apne betay ke kuch kaam aeye. aur nah beta baap ke kuch kaam aasakay. bay shak khuda ka wada sacha hai pas duniya ki zindagi tum ko dhokay mein nah daal day. aur nah fraib dainay wala ( shetan ) tumhe khuda ke baray mein kisi terhan ka fraib day
  31,34,khuda hi ko qayamat ka ilm hai aur wohimeinhہ brsata hai. aur wohi ( haamla ke ) pait ki cheezon ko jaanta hai ( ke nar hai ya madah ) aur koi shakhs nahi jaanta ke woh kalkiya kaam kere ga. aur koi mutnaqas nahi jaanta ke kis sarzamen mein ussay mout aeye gi bay shak khuda hi jan-nay wala ( aur ) khabardaar hai
